description:
This is a 30 minute workout called 'Lose Fat Fast! – Get Fit With GCN's 30 Minute High Intensity Hill Climb Training' from the channel Global Cycling Network.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Burn fat with GCN's turbo training session. Get lean, burn calories and get fit with our 30 minute indoor cycling session. This workout is designed to replicate a hill intervals.

Subscribe to GCN: http://gcn.eu/SubscribeToGCN
Get exclusive GCN gear in the GCN shop! http://gcn.eu/3h

This class is ideal if you want to lose weight and get fit and have time to train before work or during your lunch break. Designed to replicate the feeling of a hill interval training session, this workout gradually ramps up to provide as much resistance as possible in the last few minutes. We can vouch for this turbo class too – we use it regularly!

Thanks to Lucy Martin (@LUCYMARTIN05), Jessie Walker (@jesiwak) and Emily Collins (@EmilyCollins_NZ) for joining us!
